<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q31_v1" title="Q31_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Para inscribirse en un gimnasio, una persona paga una matrícula única de $15 000 y contrata, para el mismo mes, tres planes básicos y tres planes premium. En total paga $62 700.</p>
    <p>Cada plan premium cuesta $600 más que un plan básico. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> representa el precio, en pesos, de un plan básico, ¿cuál de las siguientes ecuaciones permite determinar su valor?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta ecuación representa 3 planes básicos y solo 1 plan premium, porque 3x + (x + 600) + 15 000 = 4x + 15 600. El enunciado dice 3 planes básicos y 3 planes premium, por lo que debe aparecer 3x + 3(x + 600) + 15 000 = 6x + 16 800.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La ecuación suma exactamente los 3 planes básicos, los 3 planes premium y la matrícula única: 3x + 3(x + 600) + 15 000 = 62 700. Al desarrollar, queda 3x + 3x + 1 800 + 15 000 = 62 700, es decir, 6x + 16 800 = 62 700, que corresponde exactamente a la información del problema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aquí la matrícula queda dentro del paréntesis y se multiplica por 3. Al desarrollar, 3x + 3(x + 600 + 15 000) = 3x + 3x + 1 800 + 45 000 = 6x + 46 800. Pero la matrícula es única, así que solo debe sumarse una vez: 15 000, no 45 000.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>600</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta ecuación suma 6x + 600 + 15 000 = 6x + 15 600, pero los 3 planes premium aportan 3(x + 600) = 3x + 1 800. Por eso, el total correcto debe ser 3x + 3(x + 600) + 15 000 = 6x + 16 800, no 6x + 15 600.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar qué representa cada expresión</strong></p>
            <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> es el precio de un plan básico, entonces un plan premium cuesta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Expresar el costo de los planes contratados</strong></p>
            <p>Tres planes básicos cuestan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Tres planes premium cuestan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Además, se paga una matrícula única de <m:math><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Plantear la ecuación del total pagado</strong></p>
            <p>Como en total paga <m:math><m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn></m:math>, la ecuación correcta es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Esta corresponde a la alternativa <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Verificar desarrollando la ecuación</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1800</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>62&#160;700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Determinar el valor de</strong> <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></p>
            <p>Restando <m:math><m:mn>16&#160;800</m:mn></m:math> a ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Dividiendo por <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7650</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La ecuación que permite determinar el precio de un plan básico es la alternativa <strong>B</strong>, y ese precio es <strong>$7 650</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>